        <Parent_String>compounds (materials) [300246922], materials by chemical form [300247255], materials by form [300014611], materials (substances) [300010358], Materials (hierarchy name) [300010357], Materials Facet [300264091]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
